        FROM [AspNetUsers] AS [user]
        WHERE [user].[Id] = @__id_0)
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END

SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [notification].[Id], [notification].[DateTime], [notification].[IsRead], [notification].[Text], [notification].[Type], [notification].[UserId]
